content.text: Now I need to find members who incurred expenses in more than one event, and check who paid the most among them. The expense table links to budget, and budget links to event.

sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claimdb/test_dbs/student_club.sqlite" "
SELECT e.link_to_member, COUNT(DISTINCT b.link_to_event) AS num_events, SUM(e.cost) AS total_cost
FROM expense e
JOIN budget b ON e.link_to_budget = b.budget_id
GROUP BY e.link_to_member
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT b.link_to_event) > 1
ORDER BY total_cost DESC;
"
